to the treaty bodies, including the Human Rights Committee and the 
Committee against Torture (Montenegro) / Submit promptly all due reports to 
international treaty bodies (Slovenia) / Submit the expected reports to the 
Human Rights Committee and the Committee against Torture as soon as 
