<p>112. <b>The following recommendations will be examined by Mali, which will provide 
responses in due time, but no later than the twenty-third session of the Human Rights 
Council in June 2013:</b> 
</p>
<p>112.1 <b>Ratify the Optional Protocol to the International Covenant on 
Economic, Social and Cultural Rights (Portugal); </b></p>


<p><b>20</b> GE.13-11815 
</p>
<p>112.2<b> Look into ratifying the Second Optional Protocol to the International 
Covenant on Civil and Political Rights, aiming at the abolition of the death 
