</b>112.17<b> Adopt measures to ban FGM and enhance the awareness campaign, in 
accordance with the United Nations General Assembly&#8217;s recent resolutions 
(Italy); 
</b>112.18<b> Enact legislation prohibiting all forms of traditional practice of FGM 
in line with recommendations made by CEDAW and the Committee on the 
Rights of the Child (Montenegro); 
</b>112.19<b> Take adequate measures to eradicate FGM (Netherlands); 
</b>112.20<b> Urgently adopt legislation to ban FGM (Portugal); 
</b>112.21<b> Take all feasible measures to protect children from recruitment by 
State-allied and non-State armed groups, including contributing information, 
